msgid ""
"The Options window opens. Locate and click the :guilabel:`System` tab "
"link."
msgstr ""

#: ../../userguide/gettingstarted.rst:25
msgid ""
"Locate the **TIMEZONE** parameter and use the pulldown menu to locate "
"your Timezone."
msgstr ""

